仲畀人上車，你知唔知安全措施點搞，你漏緊油呀，仲畀人上車，係唔係傻㗎你呀！」司機對張堅庭的說法充耳不聞，只拿着地拖繼續抹，張堅庭在情急之下，越講越大聲：「你唔可以畀佢哋上車，仲漏緊油，你有冇搞錯呀！叫佢哋走，叫佢哋落車啦！」<br />\n<br />\n救返幾十個愛國人士"},{"pid":"d819bdbba7a6b866e5e749c62da9faf96343a8b5","tid":1235318,"uid":82152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:31:11.000Z","msg":"痴撚線好彩冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7109b48b4f9eeb8bbe931950b99be9d81766b9ea","tid":1235318,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:31:56.000Z","msg":"二百萬定幾十萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faad1021cfe721424bbb359a2f8be716fb0234a7","tid":1235318,"uid":35410,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c518042de097969f50d705b5c6657e1fc809783f","tid":1235318,"uid":3581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:16:41.000Z","msg":"咁打火機點唔點得著柴油"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:31:58.000Z","msg":"唔得<br />\n柴油要高溫高壓力下霧化咗先會著火"},{"pid":"e193d01d9c49baf75d46e566338e26c139727005","tid":1235318,"uid":231040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:32:45.000Z","msg":"【反送中過後】屌你老味!!! 下星期就係《國歌法》二讀嘞....<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cPCuBS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cPCuBS</a>"},{"pid":"259cb201fb76f249debed2a53334828237124bfa","tid":1235318,"uid":252854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:34:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd1bf81cbb3d05ef6c7bd1945634ad39a9f484d5","tid":1235318,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:02:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4151c8c54798440afd01898242a2df079fab62b2","tid":1235318,"uid":236538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T01:42:53.000Z","msg":"要睇 推"}]}